thread.title: Cars.com Agrees to Appoint Two Starboard Nominees to Board

author: Allison Prang
title: Cars.com Agrees to Appoint Two Starboard Nominees to Board

organizations.name: cars.com agrees to appoint two starboard nominees to board cars.com inc.

text:
Cars.com Inc. said Friday it would appoint two of the nominees chosen by Starboard Value LP to its board, a month after the activist investor nominated four of its own candidates.
Cars.com said it would appoint Bryan Wiener and Michael Kelly to its board after its annual shareholder meeting. Mr. Wiener, executive chairman of 360i LLC, and Mr. Kelly, the chief executive of Kelly Newman Ventures LLC, were two of the four people Starboard said last month it would nominate to the online automotive marketplace companyâ€™s board.
